Package com.mdsol.skyfire

Class StateMachineAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mdsol.skyfire.ModelAccessor
      • com.mdsol.skyfire.StateMachineAccessor
  • public class StateMachineAccessor
extends ModelAccessor
    A class that provides functions to access UML State Machine models. Classes in Acceleo are used to be helpers to access the models.
    Version:
    1.0 Nov 28, 2012
    Author:
    Nan Li

      • getInitialStates

        public static java.util.List<org.eclipse.uml2.uml.Pseudostate> getInitialStates​(org.eclipse.uml2.uml.Region region)
        Gets all objects of Pseudostate in the region
        Parameters:
        region - a Region of a UML behavioral diagram
        Returns:
        a list of Pseudostate in the region Initial states in state machine diagrams are of Pseudostate, in this method, each object of Pseudostate is examined. If an object of Pseudostate is connected with other states, it is treated to be an initial state.
